To check whether the angle given by the user will make an triangle  or not

x=eval(input("Enter 1st angle : "))
y=eval(input("Enter 2nd angle : "))
z=eval(input("Enter 3rd angle : "))
if((x+y+z)==180):
  print("It forms a triangle")
else:
  print("It doesnt form a triangle")



************************************
OUTPUT
Enter 1st angle : 45
Enter 2nd angle : 5
Enter 3rd angle : 98
It doesnt form a triangle
***********************************
